snippet.title: Shop Keep   Trailer 2
snippet.description:
OUTDATED***************************
Shop Keep is the story of an NPC that we all encounter in our everyday Role Playing games, he always has general goods for us when we need it, always has potions and weapons ready to be sold at prices that are always fair! This is the game where we drop the N from NPC of a shop keeper, and let you supply the adventurers.

IndieDB: http://www.indiedb.com/games/shop-keep
Twitter: @strangefiredev
Website: http://www.strangefire.eu
